> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"712a7e835b07c77b667826ee9efef41fd74ae4d6","tid":317281,"uid":17531,"like":72,"dislike":0,"score":72,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T12:54:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"11475680c1033fe5d35b06ce5c1b735224648d8e","tid":317281,"uid":9607,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T12:55:26.000Z","msg":"天牛係昆蟲界嘅老虎，昆蟲中食物鏈嘅頂峰<br />\n<br />\n放咗佢啦"},{"pid":"650a160837b3e2f336a527f63ad24170e64b3a51","tid":317281,"uid":19209,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T13:01:13.000Z","msg":"樓主仲毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e533db8d00f28e3cdd3b0fe19c3f492342200ee","tid":317281,"uid":3698,"like":56,"dislike":1,"score":55,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T13:01:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/11/183332_d7a6a264f7423b2378f3899467411697.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F11%2F183332_d7a6a264f7423b2378f3899467411697.jpg&h=7dd76b7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁撚大個骷髏頭你都仲要問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n陰公，咁後生就一世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c3bf6afbdd7f7488bc42e9a741d11144d68fea0","tid":317281,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T13:03:06.000Z","msg":"又幾靚喎"},{"pid":"70fa1376ca15acf6b8d8e38e4309a3f68755aa7c","tid":317281,"uid":6116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T13:03:56.000Z","msg":"留名睇樓主入廠"},{"pid":"8ee5ed1de5e208e26d7d766639569ba70e6fbbae","tid":317281,"uid":121130,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T13:04:41.000Z","msg":"天牛好似話會咬人有d毒<br />\n比較似係過敏 比佢咬過幾痛下<br />\n我用口吸反d血再洗手用酒精消毒隻手仲係到<br />\n見到唔好放生害蟲黎 <br />\n幼蟲會咬入樹心 棵樹好快死"},{"pid":"0d3e8645ad056318e532dda02ddf18b5bd50b887","tid":317281,"uid":40723,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T13:12:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>鮮豔爬蟲類小心d <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最好係爬蟲類啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n爬蟲類定節肢類啊巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我捉過一隻一模一樣嘅，俾佢咬左下左手，好撚痛<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">利申，左手已截肢</span></span></blockquote><br />\n早兩年又係俾佢咬咗下左手，結果要切丁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"702e0dd5cbe68dfdced9d1d1d5b9861ad2ace91b","tid":317281,"uid":7986,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T13:14:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c555edd9ce0a276413bbd5a22284618749a6cf6a","tid":317281,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T13:15:16.000Z","msg":"有毒小心<br />\n<br />\n唔好拍死佢<br />\n<br />\n佢D汁同強水一樣咁勁"},{"pid":"134ef923a7b011f86d09141df2ce183449109502","tid":317281,"uid":59151,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T13:16:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">天牛係昆蟲界嘅老虎，昆蟲中食物鏈嘅頂峰<br />\n</span><br />\n放咗佢啦</blockquote><br />\n唔點解呢句好型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de87a8ee5cf599e975cf6146f1bb567c6ce878e1","tid":317281,"uid":119568,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T13:17:30.000Z","msg":"樓主變左截肢類動物未？"},{"pid":"7f0d346b65e33a94d6c92de68f05799778a781a2","tid":317281,"uid":87428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T13:31:22.000Z","msg":"甲蟲既一種"},{"pid":"47ff90863bf54731b7ac6ba9befd13ddcab012c6","tid":317281,"uid":69083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T13:39:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/q3h4xcmk\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fq3h4xcmk&h=72d0e883&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2日前係門口見到，完全唔驚人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3d03b9bc5e46c28fb65418aa14b7f4da30a3097","tid":317281,"uid":3549,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T13:43:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">天牛係昆蟲界嘅老虎，昆蟲中食物鏈嘅頂峰<br />\n</span><br />\n放咗佢啦</blockquote><br />\n唔點解呢句好型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係真唔係阿 甲蟲王者同佢打邊個贏?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8926edfa1d148b27b23d1c2c85393638d348364","tid":317281,"uid":125559,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T13:44:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>天牛係昆蟲界嘅老虎，昆蟲中食物鏈嘅頂峰<br />\n<br />\n放咗佢啦</blockquote><br />\n隻野肯定唔係本土品種，一定係人養嘅。放喺公園影響生態(佢哋食樹皮)，隻野有可能會唔適應環境死，不如試吓自己養。放咗幾款葉(屋企有種盆栽)，希望佢盡快肯食嘢。<br />\n我有上網搵過黃紋天牛鍾意食朴樹，但係無奈我暫時搵唔到。<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/11/214344_78c81f2714761f389acd07cb5a32ab52.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F11%2F214344_78c81f2714761f389acd07cb5a32ab52.jpg&h=12961c78&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6addb84164fd42d05c90f24b3c701cd123518883","tid":317281,"uid":125559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T13:46:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有毒小心<br />\n<br />\n唔好拍死佢<br />\n<br />\n佢D汁同強水一樣咁勁</blockquote><br />\n我唔會拍死佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"082ad0e154a6e9c9a1c0614ff338d5b370a7705c","tid":317281,"uid":104579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T13:47:37.000Z","msg":"放返走佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a1412a6bcd489f7d8d8cb8324b1b29b2416c49f","tid":317281,"uid":125559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T13:47:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>鮮豔爬蟲類小心d <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最好係爬蟲類啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n爬蟲類定節肢類啊巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我捉過一隻一模一樣嘅，俾佢咬左下左手，好撚痛<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">利申，左手已截肢</span></span></blockquote><br />\n早兩年又係俾佢咬咗下左手，結果要切丁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我有帶手套<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f57cfe638ee8faf832bcdd442b2b348911795fb","tid":317281,"uid":67551,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T13:51:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>天牛係昆蟲界嘅老虎，昆蟲中食物鏈嘅頂峰<br />\n<br />\n放咗佢啦</blockquote><br />\n隻野肯定唔係本土品種，一定係人養嘅。放喺公園影響生態(佢哋食樹皮)，隻野有可能會唔適應環境死，不如試吓自己養。放咗幾款葉(屋企有種盆栽)，希望佢盡快肯食嘢。<br />\n我有上網搵過黃紋天牛鍾意食朴樹，但係無奈我暫時搵唔到。<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/11/214344_78c81f2714761f389acd07cb5a32ab52.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F11%2F214344_78c81f2714761f389acd07cb5a32ab52.jpg&h=12961c78&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />加油<br />\n<br />\nbtw你對焦咁廢嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efaeb8648e6d9e77a27e7e959f526b5b0f6ef25c","tid":317281,"uid":113178,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T13:57:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 下世小心"},{"pid":"1d91569ccff09b285b1648ca18746c9768d4c5da","tid":317281,"uid":10671,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T13:57:46.000Z","msg":"RIP"},{"pid":"f90382db9afd61d993573bb75d64986e4e64149a","tid":317281,"uid":120484,"like":1,"dislike":1